%% Diagram: INP phases mapped to pipeline work
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant M as Main thread
    participant C as Compositor
    participant V as Viz / GPU

    U->>M: Input event (tap, key, click)
    Note over M: Input delay<br/>(blocked by long tasks,<br/>style, layout)
    M->>M: Run event handler
    Note over M: Processing time<br/>(JS in listener)
    M->>M: Style, layout, paint for changed DOM
    M->>C: Commit (property trees + display lists)
    C->>C: Layerize, raster, activate
    C->>V: Compositor frame
    V->>V: Aggregate + draw
    V-->>U: Next paint visible
    Note over U,V: Presentation delay<br/>(commit through draw)
